headline: Does Trimble (TRMB) Have the Potential to Rally 26.5% as Wall Street Analysts Expect?
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 26.5% in Trimble (TRMB). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
